---
import IconBrandInstagram from "./icons/IconBrandInstagram.astro";
import IconBrandLinkedin from "./icons/IconBrandLinkedin.astro";
import IconBrandWhatsapp from "./icons/IconBrandWhatsapp.astro";
---

<section
  id="contacto"
  class="py-20 md:py-28 text-center bg-delfos-bg-light dark:bg-delfos-bg-dark transition-colors duration-500"
>
  <h2 class="font-serif-title text-3xl md:text-4xl text-gold font-bold mb-6">
    ¿Listo para potenciar tu marca?
  </h2>
  <p
    class="mb-8 text-lg text-delfos-black/90 dark:text-delfos-bg-light/80 max-w-xl mx-auto"
  >
    Contactanos y descubrí cómo podemos transformar tu presencia digital.
    Respondemos siempre en el día.
  </p>
  <a
    href="mailto:studiodelfos11@gmail.com"
    class="inline-block bg-gold text-delfos-bg-dark dark:text-delfos-bg-light px-8 py-3 rounded-full font-semibold shadow-lg hover:scale-105 focus-visible:ring-2 ring-gold transition-transform duration-300 mb-8 md:mb-4"
    aria-label="Enviar email a Delfos Studio"
  >
    Escribinos
  </a>
  <div
    class="flex justify-center gap-5 md:gap-6 mt-6 md:mt-8"
    role="navigation"
    aria-label="Redes sociales Delfos Studio"
  >
    <a
      href="https://instagram.com/delfosstudio"
      target="_blank"
      rel="noopener noreferrer"
      class="text-gold hover:text-gold-80 transition-all duration-200 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-gold/60 rounded-full"
      aria-label="Instagram"
      title="Instagram"
    >
      <IconBrandInstagram
        class="w-8 h-8 hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-150"
      />
    </a>
    <a
      href="https://linkedin.com/company/delfosstudio"
      target="_blank"
      rel="noopener noreferrer"
      class="text-gold hover:text-gold-80 transition-all duration-200 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-gold/60 rounded-full"
      aria-label="LinkedIn"
      title="LinkedIn"
    >
      <IconBrandLinkedin
        class="w-8 h-8 hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-150"
      />
    </a>
    <a
      href="https://wa.me/+5492324592391"
      target="_blank"
      rel="noopener noreferrer"
      class="text-gold hover:text-gold-80 transition-all duration-200 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-gold/60 rounded-full"
      aria-label="WhatsApp"
      title="WhatsApp"
    >
      <IconBrandWhatsapp
        class="w-8 h-8 hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-150"
      />
    </a>
  </div>
  <p
    class="text-xs mt-10 text-delfos-black/40 dark:text-delfos-bg-light/50 max-w-md mx-auto"
  >
    También podés encontrarnos en redes sociales o agendar una videollamada
    cuando quieras.
  </p>
</section>
